description: Demolition of all existing buildings and the construction of five buildings ranging in height from 3 storeys to 19 storeys plus plant (to maximum height of 70.15m AOD) for mixed use purposes to provide 379 residential units (Class C3), 240sqm of retail space (A1, A2 and A3), 201sqm of concierge/management space plus 195sqm of ancillary leisure and 247sqm of meeting room/ function space for the occupiers of the development, car parking, landscaping, new vehicular and pedestrian access points and other ancillary work (Amended Scheme).
